data.description: SELLER IS OFFERING UP TO A $10,000 BUYER CREDIT TOWARD CLOSING COSTS OR RATE BUY DOWN! Located in one of the premiere communities in SE Ocala, this POOL HOME is move in ready with so many upgrades not found with new construction.  Pulling up to the custom designed pavered driveway, you can't help but admire the well manicured custom landscaping, covered front entry, vinyl privacy fencing.  Stepping through the front door, the pride of ownership is evident with the custom plank flooring, recessed lighting.  You won't be able to resist your dream kitchen with a built in coffee bar with its own mini fridge, island breakfast bar, stainless appliances, numerous cabinets and vast counterspace and the walk in pantry with the custom etched glass door.  At the end of your busy, relax in the oversized principal suite with tray ceilings, walk in closets, and spa like bath featuring a large walk in shower, dual vanities and separate water closet.  The covered patio with the screened in pool offers a ton of fun for all your family and friends year round.  Storage shed gives you plenty of space for your pool and lawn equipment.  Close to major highways, and conveniently located between Ocala and The Villages.  Florida living at its finest!
